OL,3,CMoment PC killer was brought home to
OL,4,Cface justice
OL,6,FFootage has been released by police
OL,7,Fshowing the moment a robbery
OL,8,Fmastermind was placed in UK custody
OL,9,Fover the murder of PC Sharon
OL,10,FBeshenivsky after an international
OL,11,Fmanhunt.
OL,13,FPiran Ditta Khan had evaded capture
OL,14,Ffor more than 14 years after the
OL,15,Fmurder of the West Yorkshire officer
OL,16,Fin Bradford in 2005.
OL,18,FBut, after being arrested in Pakistan
OL,19,Fin 2020, he was finally extradited in
OL,20,F2023.
