OL,3,CMoment PC killer was brought home to
OL,4,Cface justice
OL,6,FKhan, now 75, has now been convicted
OL,7,Fof murder following a trial.
OL,9,FFootage released by West Yorkshire
OL,10,FPolice after the guilty verdict shows
OL,11,Fhim limping from a patrol car before
OL,12,Fbeing booked into custody at Elland
OL,13,FRoad police station in Leeds.
OL,15,FA police officer tells Khan: "Piran
OL,16,FDitta Khan, (the allegation is that)
OL,17,Fon the 18th day of November 2005 you
OL,18,Fmurdered police constable Sharon
OL,19,FBeshenivsky."
