OL,6,FAnother person can be heard saying:
OL,7,F"Have you any reply to that charge? Do
OL,8,Fyou wish to say anything?
OL,10,FHe replies: "I...I never murdered
OL,11,Fanybody."
OL,13,FHe is then locked in a cell.
OL,15,FPC Beshenivsky, a 38-year-old mother-
OL,16,Fof-three, had only been working for
OL,17,Fthe force for nine months when she was
OL,18,Fshot dead after responding to reports
OL,19,Fof a raid at Universal Express travel
OL,20,Fagents on Morley Street, Bradford, on
OL,21,F18 November 2005.
