OL,3,CMoment PC killer was brought home to
OL,4,Cface justice
OL,6,FHer colleague PC Teresa Milburn was
OL,7,Falso shot but survived.
OL,9,FKhan fled the country in early 2006.
OL,11,FHe was the last of seven men to face
OL,12,Ftrail. Three others have already been
OL,13,Fconvicted of murder, two of
OL,14,Fmanslaughter and a sixth of robbery.
OL,16,FAfter four days of deliberations, a
OL,17,Fjury at Leeds Crown Court found Khan
OL,18,Fguilty by a majority verdict.
OL,20,FHe will be sentenced at a later date.
